00:23:34,518 --> 00:23:38,488
This is, it's a Valmont Executive.

512
00:23:38,489 --> 00:23:40,190
It is my family's brand.

513
00:23:40,191 --> 00:23:41,658
It is, it is only the rarest

514
00:23:41,659 --> 00:23:44,995
