00:24:06,650 --> 00:24:07,650
That's healthy.

525
00:24:09,252 --> 00:24:10,754
<i>As the day wore on,</i>

526
00:24:10,755 --> 00:24:12,523
<i>Beatrice was playing hard to get.</i>

527
00:24:13,523 --> 00:24:18,260
<i>Conrad's pseudo-intellectual
