00:28:10,693 --> 00:28:13,863
<i>Conrad walked into a room,</i>

565
00:28:13,864 --> 00:28:15,832
<i>the way he waved his hands in the air</i>

566
00:28:15,833 --> 00:28:19,469
<i>every time he heard Bach, the
