569
00:28:25,576 --> 00:28:29,278
<i>and a single Windsor knot,</i>

570
00:28:29,279 --> 00:28:31,847
<i>his infallible wit and charm</i>

571
00:28:31,848 --> 00:28:35,585
<i>and the way he used words
